fig--title-label\">Figure 1. </span>Meter Start and Sweep Angles</figcaption>\n<img alt=\"Image\" class=\"image\" id=\"wxw1665702646699__image_pyf_wsk_zwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/metersweep.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"wxw1665702646699__section_x5w_wsk_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d969522e95\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bwv1665702644903.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bwv1665702644903.html\" title=\"The umeter widget displays the value of a Numeric field on a gauge for which there is a predefined range of values marked around the outer edge. Uniface provides a logical widget called Meter, which is mapped to umeter.\">umeter (Meter)</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616840\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616840\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTop